==English==
===Verb===
'''articulated'''
# Simple past and past participle of ''to [[articulate]]''.

===Adjective===
'''articulated'''
# Constructed with one or more pivoted joints which allow bending of an otherwise rigid structure.
# Specifically, describes a vehicle with such joints, e.g. an [[articulated lorry]], [[articulated bus]], or certain kinds of [[streetcar]]s and [[train]]s.